Wash and dry produce. Wrap @demi-baguette{2} loosely in #paper towels{}; microwave for
~{30%seconds}.

Trim and slice @zucchini{2} lengthwise into 1/4-inch-thick planks. Slice @tomato{1}
into 1/4-inch-thick rounds.

Lightly drizzle zucchini with @olive oil{1%tsp}; season with @salt{} and @pepper{}.
Place on a #microwave-safe plate{}; microwave until steamed, ~{3%minutes}.

While zucchini steams, halve baguettes lengthwise. Spread @pesto{4%tbsp} onto cut sides.

Top bottom halves of baguettes with @burrata{4%oz}; slice into burrata to spread.
Top with zucchini. Fan tomato over top and drizzle with @balsamic glaze{5%tsp}. Close
sandwiches and serve.